text: More media hyperbole. Dramatic headlines and sound bytes substitute for deep dives intended to attract and interest the audience. We are all momentum players now - miles long but only inches deep.
There is a universal optimism in the business media. But, remember Bob Farrell: "Excesses in one direction will lead to an opposite excess in the other direction."
